  "title": "Sales Manager – Marine & Offshore",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking an experienced <strong>Sales Manager</strong> to join a well-established company in the <strong>marine industry</strong>, specializing in wire ropes, synthetic ropes, shackles, and lifting equipment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop and maintain strong relationships with customers in the shipyard and marine sectors.</li>\n  <li>Proactively generate new sales leads through cold calling, client visits, and trade shows.</li>\n  <li>Promote company products and provide professional advice to customers.</li>\n  <li>Prepare quotations, proposals, and follow-ups to close sales.</li>\n  <li>Report sales activities and updates to the Director daily.</li>\n  <li>Support strategy planning and assist in developing new market segments.</li>\n  <li>Provide guidance and training to new or junior team members when needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No. 20C0270</p>",
